data.text:
Hi everyone!

Breast cancer and ovarian cancer is way too prevalent in society and we’re raising awareness and funds about the illness to help with early intervention and prevention where we can!

Please support our efforts by making a secure online donation and by posting a message of support.

Donations made through this platform are secure and will be remitted directly through to my charity of choice. Thanks so much for your support!
